WEBVTT

00:00:00.880 --> 00:00:07.000
Jehovah chose the young woman Mary for a difficult assignment.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:12.720
It was a unique assignment, one that required great faith.

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:21.000
It was to care for and raise the only begotten Son of God, Jesus Christ.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:25.239
What an amazing privilege that was.

00:00:25.239 --> 00:00:30.600
And yet it required strong faith on the part of Mary, not only because this was a

00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:36.640
very serious responsibility that would involve quite a number of years, but

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:43.679
initially, Mary before accepting this assignment, had some concerns no doubt.

00:00:43.679 --> 00:00:48.600
One of them would have been the concern with regard to the reaction of her

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:54.240
friends, neighbors, relatives, and, yes, of course, her fiance Joseph.

00:00:54.240 --> 00:00:59.520
After all, the angel didn't say to her, don't worry, I'll go and inform this of

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:04.200
all the to all the ones involved so that they don't get upset.

00:01:04.200 --> 00:01:09.959
So it was a very difficult and overwhelming assignment for Mary.

00:01:09.959 --> 00:01:13.439
Can you imagine how she approached this assignment?

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:19.469
Well, to help us do that, let's watch this short video.

00:01:19.469 --> 00:01:21.909
I was engaged to Mary Joseph.

00:01:21.909 --> 00:01:29.390
I thought we would have a simple and quiet life, and then suddenly everything changed.

00:01:29.390 --> 00:01:35.909
I know that God sometimes asks us to do what is difficult, but this seemed impossible beyond

00:01:35.909 --> 00:01:38.030
anything we could handle.

00:01:38.030 --> 00:01:41.870
But I knew I was safe in Jehovah's hands.

00:01:41.870 --> 00:01:48.310
If we remain loyal to Him and did our best to care for His precious Son, He would always

00:01:48.310 --> 00:01:52.310
be loyal to us and give us what we needed.

00:01:52.310 --> 00:02:01.450
Yes, when we think of Mary's situation, all she was interested in was having a quiet,

00:02:01.450 --> 00:02:06.129
simple life, then suddenly everything changed for her.

00:02:06.129 --> 00:02:12.050
And it may have seemed impossible for her to be able to accept that assignment.

00:02:12.050 --> 00:02:14.009
And yet, what was her reaction?

