Luke, Jehovah's slave girl, may it happen to me according to your declaration.

00:02:37.370 --> 00:02:45.009
Yes, in full faith and with humility, she accepted this difficult assignment.

00:02:45.009 --> 00:02:50.650
She knew that Jehovah would be with her and that he would help her.

00:02:50.650 --> 00:02:54.210
But what was it that gave Mary such a strong faith?

00:02:54.930 --> 00:03:01.009
Well, we get a clue if we look down in the same chapter, but verse 46.

00:03:01.009 --> 00:03:04.569
So that's Luke chapter 1 and verse 46.

