00:04:24.970 --> 00:04:31.930
So yes, Mary had strong faith that was based on the Holy writings, and that is what made

00:04:31.930 --> 00:04:35.129
her qualified for this assignment.

00:04:35.129 --> 00:04:38.250
Well, what about us?

00:04:38.250 --> 00:04:43.129
How can we imitate this strong faith of Mary?

